reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 25, 2023
reviews.reviewText: The quality is better than I expected for the cost! I thought that this was going to be some cheap costume jewelry that will turn your skin green. Nope, I was able to wear every piece, from necklace to earrings to rings without a reaction for days. This is from someone who can only wear real silver! Anything else breaks me out.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 21, 2023
reviews.reviewText: These are such good quality! The rings are adjustable so they fit any size finger. Since they are such good quality, it's a little tough trying to adjust the rings to fit my finger exactly, but I am glad I have that option! The necklace/bracelet extender is very nice to have since most necklaces are made to fit like a choker or for smaller necks. The bracelets are very simple but very cute and adjustable! Would totally recommend!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 13, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars A great starter set
reviews.reviewText: This is a great starter set for any jewelry collection. There was a lot of variety, and I love that it came with different necklaces, bracelets, rings, and earrings. All of these pieces can easily be stacked, but they make great statement pieces all on their own as well. The material itself, particularly on the rings, feels rather thin/pliable, so I'm not sure how much use they will get before they lose their shape or break. All the chains on the bracelets and necklaces do feel more sturdy, though. All pieces are perfect for accommodating different size wrists and fingers; the bracelets are either stretchy or have multiple links in the chain to pick the perfect place for the clasp, and the rings are all open on the back to easily fit different finger circumferences. All these pieces are great for everyday wear, and they're the perfect staples to start or expand any jewelry collection.
